Guotai Junan Prepares for China’s First Hedge Fund, Reuters Says

-- B y   J o s h u a   F e l l m a n
-- 
2011-02-14T17:57:02Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-14/guotai-junan-prepares-for-china-s-first-hedge-fund-reuters-says.html
Guotai Junan Securities Co. is
preparing to start  China ’s first officially approved hedge fund,
Reuters said, citing President Zhang Biao. The firm plans to
raise 300 million yuan ($45 million) initially, the news agency
said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
